        "category": "Faculty Advisor",
        "bio": "Associate Professor in the Department of Mathematics at Thapar Institute of Engineering and Technology, Patiala, where he has been serving since 2009. He obtained his Ph.D. in Mathematical Programming from Panjab University, Chandigarh in 2012. His research focuses on optimization theory and mathematical programming, with particular emphasis on linear and nonlinear optimization, integer programming, financial mathematics, and portfolio optimization.",
